    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 76-77.</p><p>Quickened Blast</p><p>Prerequisite: Level 20+ Warlock, a Warlock Cantrip That Deals Damage</p><p>Choose a warlock cantrip that deals damage with a casting time of 1 action. That cantrip now has a casting time of 1 bonus action instead. If you use the chosen cantrip to perform a Legendary Blast, you can perform that Legendary Blast as a bonus action.</p><p>Repeatable. You can gain this invocation more than once. Each time you do so, choose a different eligible cantrip.</p></div>",
